OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775070658
OL,3,CBakery closes after 109 years due to
OL,4,C'relentless' rising costs
OL,6,FA fixture of Carlisle's high street
OL,7,Fhas closed after 109 years, blaming
OL,8,F"relentless increases in operational
OL,9,Fand ingredient costs".
OL,11,FRoutledges the Bakers announced in a
OL,12,FFacebook post on Monday morning that
OL,13,Fall of its seven branches have closed
OL,14,F"for good".
OL,16,FThe business said: "This is not
OL,17,Fsomething we ever thought we would
OL,18,Fhave to write.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
