FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775070658
OL,3,CBakery closes after 109 years due to
OL,4,C'relentless' rising costs
OL,6,F"Since the end of 2024, we have faced
OL,7,Frelentless increases in our
OL,8,Foperational and ingredient costs.
OL,10,F"Alongside this, minimum wage
OL,11,Fincreases, business rate increases and
OL,12,Fthe reality of further energy price
OL,13,Frises when we renew our contracts in
OL,14,Fthe coming months means our
OL,15,Foperational costs alone will be over
OL,16,F#80,000 higher than in 2025.
OL,18,F"At the same time, we have seen a
OL,19,Fcontinued decline in high street
OL,20,Ffootfall.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775070658
OL,3,CBakery closes after 109 years due to
OL,4,C'relentless' rising costs
OL,6,F"So, with incredibly heavy hearts, we
OL,7,Fhave made the decision not to face
OL,8,Fanother year of rising costs and
OL,9,Funcertainty. Routledges has now closed
OL,10,Ffor good after 109 years."
OL,12,FThe bakery said in its post that its
OL,13,Flatest business rates bill, delivered
OL,14,Flast week, had "risen dramatically
OL,15,Fcompared to 2025 following the removal
OL,16,Fof the 40% hospitality relief that
OL,17,Fbusinesses like ours once relied on."
OL,19,FIt added that "2025 was already one of
OL,20,Fthe toughest years we have ever
OL,21,Fendured."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
