CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775070658
OL,3,CBakery closes after 109 years due to
OL,4,C'relentless' rising costs
OL,6,FRoutledges had recently tried a new
OL,7,Fapproach to business, opening a self-
OL,8,Fservice store in Carlisle's market
OL,9,Fhall in February 2026.
OL,11,FAt the time Routledges said the move
OL,12,Fwould reduce running costs and pass on
OL,13,Fsavings to customers.
OL,15,FThe company cut its prices across its
OL,16,Fstores in March.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
